{
  "stem": "6258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And well, even in-- in school, we had a religious history of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somehow what I remembered from these things, even if there was such a big book about the history of Jews, it was the word 'Sanhedrin.' And I knew much more about the Punic Wars and about-- about [INAUDIBLE] Greece and so forth than about Jewish wars and-- and-- and the other things.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "However, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- I never feel-- had that feeling of being persecuted as a Jewish girl or being resented, except later on, just a year before the war, when I was in a state gymnasium, which was very difficult to get there.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was an exam and so forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I-- we were under five.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were about 50 girls in that class, and we were under five.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there, one day, there was something strange happen, that when we got all new coats, three of these Jewish girls had a Star of David cut out of their coat.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was such a terrible thing, that to my friend and me, who did not have that coat cut, it was even more hurtful than to other, our friends, who did.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father, who was very active in the PTA, as you would call it here, went right away to gymnasium, to the principal, and said, I am taking my daughter out of here, and she will go to a private school.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this director was very furious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said, why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is not-- she did not suffer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father said, no, I don't want them-- I don't want her to stay here one minute longer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's strange.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After the war, I attended the same gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
